data.description: This colonial home is a charming blend of traditional style and modern features. As you step inside, you are greeted by an abundance of natural light streaming in through large windows, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout the house. The open floor concept seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying time with your loved ones. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, sleek countertops, and ample storage space. Upstairs, you will find three spacious bedrooms, each offering plenty of natural light and closet space, and modern bathroom. Descending to the finished basement, you are greeted by a versatile space that can be used as a cozy family room, a home office, or a guest suite. The added convenience of a full bathroom in the basement ensures that this area is not only functional but also a comfortable extension of the living space. Overall, this colonial home is a perfect blend of classic charm and modern convenience, offering a comfortable and stylish living space for everyone. Only 35 minutes from New York City, and very close distance to the train station.
